Global Hypochlorous Acid Market Insights
Hypochlorous Acid Market Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Hypochlorous Acid Market Overview
The global hypochlorous acid market was valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2031. This growth is largely driven by increasing demand in various end-use industries, including healthcare, food processing, and water treatment. With heightened awareness around hygiene and sanitization, especially post-pandemic, hypochlorous acid is widely used for disinfecting and cleaning purposes. The rise in water treatment activities, driven by population growth and industrialization, further supports the demand for hypochlorous acid. Additionally, eco-friendly and safer disinfectants are gaining traction, with hypochlorous acid being recognized for its non-toxic properties compared to traditional chemicals.

